{"title":"Apidura Racing Aerobar Pack hangs streamlined bag under your aero extensions","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/13/apidura-racing-aerobar-pack-hangs-streamlined-bag-under-your-aero-extensions/","date":1626189697000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Apidura has reshaped a slimmer, streamlined front end for their fast ultra-distance audax bikepacking bag setup with a new Racing Aerobar Pack. Aiming for less frontal area to reduce energy-sapping drag, the new bag tucks neatly out front underneath your aero bar extensions, packing just enough gear inside, with room for snacks up top…</p><h2>Apidura Racing Aerobar Pack out-front bikepacking bag</h2><figure id=\"attachment_265089\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-265089\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111457/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_closing.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111457/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_closing.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x290/rscb25/ng:webp/ngcb25\" alt=\"Apidura Racing Aerobar Pack out-front aero bar extension bikepacking bag, front\" width=\"1500\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111457/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_closing.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111457/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_closing-297x178.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111457/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_closing-800x480.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:we