s.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111457/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_closing-800x480.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111457/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_closing-120x72.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111457/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_closing-768x461.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111457/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_closing-696x418.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111457/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_closing-1068x641.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111457/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_closing-700x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 700w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-265089\">c. Apidura</figcaption></figure><p>Pretty much a cross between their Expedition Fork Pack and a Racing Saddle Pack, the new Aerobar Pack is a relatively small 2.5L roll-top bag that tucks under your extensions, with by far Apidura’s smallest frontal area for a handlebar pack yet. Apidura says its development actually came directly from seeing “<em>enough racers mounting our fork packs to their aerobars&nbsp;to realise that there’s a real unmet need amongst the racing contingent</em>“.</p><h3>Less frontal area means reduced drag… aero is everything!</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth.jpg\" alt=\"Apidura Racing Aerobar Pack out-front aero bar extension bikepacking bag, packing\" width=\"1500\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth-700x420.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb25 src ng ngcb25 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111452/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_open-mouth-700x420.jpg 700w\"></a></p><p>Their first <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2018/12/03/apidura-racing-series-bikepacking-bags-slim-down-lighten-up-for-fast-travel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Racing Series Handlebar Pack</a> also hung under your aero bars to haul 5L of gear, but at about 27cm wide x 18cm tall, it kinda did feel like it was pushing into the wind – a bit against the ethos of getting low &amp; aero on the bike. The 2.5L <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/02/03/apidura-racing-handlebar-mini-pack-opens-up-easy-access-in-front-of-the-bar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Racing Handlebar Mini Pack</a> scaled that back to just 22.5x14cm, and hung directly off the tops of your dropbars, for riders prioritizing easy access to getting low.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111445/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_frontal-area-dimensions-wide.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111445/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_frontal-area-dimensions-wide.jpg\" alt=\"Apidura Racing Aerobar Pack out-front aero bar extension bikepacking bag, dimensions\" width=\"1500\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111445/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_frontal-area-dimensions-wide.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111445/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_frontal-area-dimensions-wide-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111445/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_frontal-area-dimensions-wide-800x480.jp