bar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_frontal-area-dimensions-wide-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111445/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_frontal-area-dimensions-wide-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111445/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_frontal-area-dimensions-wide-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111445/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_frontal-area-dimensions-wide-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111445/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_frontal-area-dimensions-wide-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111445/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_frontal-area-dimensions-wide-700x420.jpg 700w\"></a></p><p>Now the new Aerobar Pack adapts to your aero bar setup, with just a 9.5cm tall x max 11cm wide at the widest point of its buckles.</p><h3>Tech details</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111439/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_side.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13111439/Apidura-Racing-Aerobar-Pack-out-front-aero-bar-extension-bikepacking-bag_side.jpg\" alt=\"Apidura Racing Aerobar Pack out-front aero bar extension bikepacking bag, side\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13